==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: New Zealand
<hw>New` Zea"land</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A group of islands in the
South Pacific Ocean.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>New Zealand flax</b></col>. <sd>(a)</sd>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <cd>A tall, liliaceous herb (<spn>Phormium
tenax</spn>), having very long, sword-shaped, distichous leaves which
furnish a fine, strong fiber very valuable for cordage and the
like.</cd> <sd>(b)</sd> <cd>The fiber itself.</cd> -- <col><b>New
Zealand tea</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>a myrtaceous shrub
(<spn>Leptospermum scoparium</spn>) of New Zealand and Australia, the
leaves of which are used as a substitute for tea.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nexible</ent>⟦br⟧
